{"tid":712223,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷唔爭氣慘敗 馬勒當拿當場落淚","createTime":"2018-06-22T02:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T04:28:35.000Z","uid":156522,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae93a534c5bdb2e687b20c7cb996b78f8b8ee942","tid":712223,"uid":156522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"阿根廷昔日球王「老馬」馬勒當拿，周四在世盃D組分組賽第二輪，亦有入場支持祖國阿根廷及接班人美斯，希望國家隊能夠一舉擊敗克羅地亞，然而最終阿根廷卻以0:3慘敗，親眼目睹賽果的馬勒當拿，更由開賽前異常興奮，到最後落下男兒淚。<br />\n<br />\n在開賽前，入場睇波的馬勒當拿成為觀眾席上的焦點，而馬勒當拿亦表現得非常興奮，除了向球迷揮手外，更一度高舉美斯的球衣，呼籲球迷一同為阿根廷及美斯打氣。<br />\n<br />\n然而比賽的進展，漸漸不像馬勒當拿的預期，當阿根廷先失一球時，馬勒當拿已收起興奮的表情坐了下來，其後阿根廷接連失波，馬勒當拿直情抱頭掩面，更被鏡頭捕捉到他落下男兒淚，似乎阿根廷及接班人美斯的表現，實在傷透了老球王馬勒當拿的心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619186_3e66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619186_3e66.jpg&h=51b21662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬勒當拿起初表現興奮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619188_7a9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619188_7a9c.jpg&h=d019fb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619189_21b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619189_21b6.jpg&h=280d2adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619190_972c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619190_972c.jpg&h=733c8a96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿根廷先失一球，馬勒當拿已收起興奮表情坐下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619191_d70b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619191_d70b.jpg&h=ffdceb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬勒當拿似乎對賽果難以相信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619193_702e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619193_702e.jpg&h=b833dfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬勒當拿一度掩面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529619194_2454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529619194_2454.jpg&h=40114b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬勒當拿落下男兒淚"},{"pid":"7c4c3e611c6402043d41804ffd3b3007a3acb48d","tid":712223,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4d35233e5fff1fc05cabcb43ff3e201fef9956","tid":712223,"uid":130203,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"尋晚已經留意到, 點解佢左右手都要戴錶....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c258f830f1d8257c956a1e068a208b04b68e73","tid":712223,"uid":156522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4d35233e5fff1fc05cabcb43ff3e201fef9956","tid":712223,"uid":130203,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"尋晚已經留意到, 點解佢左右手都要戴錶....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"係 見到個下都笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ed7adaec48b019678ab0752558cce493ea36b2","tid":712223,"uid":126763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c258f830f1d8257c956a1e068a208b04b68e73","tid":712223,"uid":156522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote